headline: Snap-on Incorporated to Webcast 2024 Fourth Quarter and Full Year Results Conference Call
summary: Snap-on Incorporated will release 2024 fourth quarter and full year results prior to the market open on Thursday, February 6, 2025. A conference call to discuss the results will be held at 10:00 a.m....
